tball|Thursday night]] game as \"speedy delivery\" (in honor of [[David Newell|Mr. McFeely]]), their three [[West Coast of the United States|West Coast]] games as \"traveling to a far-away land\", and the series' closing theme to reference the team's [[Bye (sports)|bye week]].<ref>{{cite tweet|user=steelers|number=1118668326077698048|date=April 18, 2019|title=It\u2019s a beautiful day in the neighborhood.|accessdate=April 21, 2019}}</ref> The Steelers received critical acclaim by both ''[[USA Today]]'' and the ''[[Pittsburgh Tribune-Review]]'' for honoring Rogers.<ref>https://ftw.usatoday.com/2019/04/nfl-schedule-2019-best-twitter</ref><ref>https://triblive.com/sports/steelers-channel-mister-rogers-as-nfl-teams-get-creative-with-schedule/</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Week\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Date\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Opponent\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Result\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Record\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Venue\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| NFL.com<br>recap\n|- style=\"background:#fcc\"\n! [[#Week 1: at New England Patriots|1]]\n| September 8\n| at [[2019 New England Patriots season|New England Patriots]]\n| '''L''' 3\u201333\n| 0\u20131\n| [[Gillette Stadium]]\n| [https://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/2019090812/2019/REG1/steelers@patriots Recap]\n|- style=\"background:#fcc\"\n! [[#Week 2: vs. Seattle Seahawks|2]]\n| September 15\n| [[2019 Seattle Seahawks season|Seattle Seahawks]]\n| '''L''' 26\u201328\n| 0\u20132\n| [[Heinz Field]]\n| [https://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/2019091507/2019/REG2/seahawks@steelers Recap]\n|- style=\"background:#fcc\"\n! [[#Week 3: at San Francisco 49ers