|87|Kevin Rader|d=American football|TE}}\n{{NFLplayer|49|Christian Scotland-Williamson|TE|PS/EX}}\n{{NFLplayer|42|Ralph Webb|d=American football|RB}}\n}}\n\n==Preseason==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Week\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Date\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Opponent\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Result\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Record\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Game site\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| NFL.com<br>recap\n|- style=\"background:#cfc\"\n! 1\n| {{dow tooltip|August 9, 2019}}\n| [[2019 Tampa Bay Buccaneers season|Tampa Bay Buccaneers]]\n| '''W''' 30\u201328\n| 1\u20130\n| [[Heinz Field]]\n| [https://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/2019080952/2019/PRE1/buccaneers@steelers Recap]\n|- style=\"background:#cfc\"\n! 2\n| {{dow tooltip|August 17, 2019}}\n| [[2019 Kansas City Chiefs season|Kansas City Chiefs]]\n| '''W''' 17\u20137\n| 2\u20130\n| Heinz Field\n| [https://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/2019081754/2019/PRE2/chiefs@steelers Recap]\n|- style=\"background:#cfc\"\n! 3\n| {{dow tooltip|August 25, 2019}}\n| at [[2019 Tennessee Titans season|Tennessee Titans]]\n| '''W''' 18\u20136\n| 3\u20130\n| [[Nissan Stadium]]\n| [https://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/2019082551/2019/PRE3/steelers@titans Recap]\n|- style=\"background:#fcc\"\n! 4\n| {{dow tooltip|August 29, 2019}}\n| at [[2019 Carolina Panthers season|Carolina Panthers]]\n| '''L''' 19\u201325\n| 3\u20131\n| [[Bank of America Stadium]]\n| [https://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/2019082952/2019/PRE4/steelers@panthers Recap]\n|}\n\n==Regular season==\n===Schedule===\nThe Steelers, along with the rest of the NFL, unveiled their schedule on April 17. The team released a video on [[social media]] unveiling their schedule by using the Neighborhood of Make-Believe from ''[[Mister Rogers' Neighborhood]]'' in honor of Pittsburgh native [[Fred Rogers]]. Longtime [[Pittsburgh Steelers Radio Network|radio]] play-by-play announcer [[Bill Hillgrove]] did the voiceover, referring to the [[AFC North|Steelers division rivals]] as their \"neighbors\", their [[Thursday Night Football|Thursday night]] game as \"speedy delivery\" (in honor of [[David Newell|Mr. McFeely]]), their three [[West Coast of the United States|West Coast]] games as \"traveling to a far-away land\", and the series' closing theme to reference the team's [[Bye (sports)|bye week]].<ref>{{cite tweet|user=steelers|number=1118668326077698048|date=April 18, 2019|title=It\u2019s a beautiful day in the neighborhood.|accessdate=April 21, 2019}}</ref> The Steelers received critical acclaim by both ''[[USA Today]]'' and the ''[[Pittsburgh Tribune-Review]]'' for honoring Rogers.<ref>https://ftw.usatoday.com/2019/04/nfl-schedule-2019-best-twitter</ref><ref>https://triblive.com/sports/steelers-channel-mister-rogers-as-nfl-teams-get-creative-with-schedule/</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Week\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Date\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Opponent\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Result\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Record\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Venue\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Pittsburgh Steelers|year=2019|border=2}}\"| NFL.com<br>recap\n|- style=\"background:#fcc\"\n! [[#Week 1: at New England Patriots|1]]\n| September 8\n| at [[2019 New England Patriots season|New England Patriots]]\n| '''L''' 3\u201333\n| 0\u20131\n| [[Gillette Stadium]]\n| [https://www.nfl.com/g